{"aid": "inj0qe7d7lf2yr", "result": {"folders": ["lecture18"], "unique_views": 53, "no_answer": 0, "change_log": [{"data": "ing6quz6a7c4oo", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-25T15:55:37Z", "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "type": "create"}, {"data": "ing718owqx81xr", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-25T16:03:41Z", "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "type": "update"}, {"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "data": "inhm674d7vf4j1", "when": "2016-04-26T15:55:13Z", "to": "ing6qux3zqi4om", "anon": "no", "type": "i_answer"}, {"to": "ing6qux3zqi4om", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-26T16:00:56Z", "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "type": "followup"}, {"to": "ing6qux3zqi4om", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-27T00:56:27Z", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "type": "feedback"}, {"to": "ing6qux3zqi4om", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-27T02:32:56Z", "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "type": "followup"}, {"to": "ing6qux3zqi4om", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-27T02:41:58Z", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "type": "feedback"}, {"to": "ing6qux3zqi4om", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-27T02:49:41Z", "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "type": "followup"}, {"to": "ing6qux3zqi4om", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-27T02:53:38Z", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "type": "feedback"}, {"to": "ing6qux3zqi4om", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-27T02:55:48Z", "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "type": "feedback"}, {"to": "ing6qux3zqi4om", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-27T03:29:40Z", "uid": "i0ccfx63sir1e", "type": "followup"}, {"to": "ing6qux3zqi4om", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-27T03:38:57Z", "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "type": "feedback"}], "upvote_ids": [], "id": "ing6qux3zqi4om", "bookmarked": 5, "no_answer_followup": 0, "i_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "children": [{"folders": [], "is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2016-04-26T15:55:13Z", "config": {}, "tag_endorse_arr": [], "children": [], "bucket_name": "Today", "type": "i_answer", "tag_endorse": [], "bucket_order": 2, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "id": "inhm67495oc4j0", "history": [{"content": "<p>一个粗略的回复如下&#xff1a;</p>\n<p>由于PV操作的配对关系分散在不同进程中&#xff0c;其正确性判断是很困难的。管程基于面向对象的思路&#xff0c;把PV操作封装在管程的实现中&#xff0c;使用者可以不考虑或少考虑PV操作的配对和同步关系的正确性&#xff0c;减少了同步关系正确性判断的困难。这可以理解为“面向对象的方法把相关的数据和处理函数封装到一起&#xff0c;可减少程序出错的可能”。另一种说法是&#xff0c;不用goto语句的程序出错的可能性会少。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>如果还有疑惑&#xff0c;请继续提问。</p>", "anon": "no", "subject": "", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "created": "2016-04-26T15:55:13Z"}]}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-26T16:00:56Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "created": "2016-04-26T16:00:56Z", "type": "followup", "d-bucket": "Yesterday", "id": "inhmdkdywcm1cp", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Yesterday", "no_answer": 0, "config": {}, "bucket_order": 3, "data": null, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-27T00:56:27Z", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "created": "2016-04-27T00:56:27Z", "type": "feedback", "id": "ini5i87yw6q3id", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>这个问题提得很好。我尝试回答如下&#xff0c;并欢迎继续置疑。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>从表达能力的角度来说&#xff0c;信号量和管程是等价的。即&#xff1a;用信号量可以实现管程&#xff0c;用管程也可以实现信号量。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>从性能的角度来说&#xff0c;通常信号量比管程好。即&#xff1a;管程中限制只能有一个进程执行的代码范围通常比实现精致的信号量方法要大。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>从使用方便或实现难度的角度来说&#xff0c;管程比信号量好用&#xff0c;出错的可能小&#xff0c;找错相对容易一些。</p>\n<p></p>"}], "subject": "<p>请问将PV操作封装后&#xff0c;wait和signal函数是否也要配对&#xff1f;如果还是需要配对的话&#xff0c;wait/signal配对和P/V配对究竟有什么本质的区别&#xff1f;谢谢老师&#xff01;</p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-27T02:32:56Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "created": "2016-04-27T02:32:56Z", "type": "followup", "no_answer": 0, "id": "ini8ybjsq3t7dc", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-27T02:41:58Z", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "created": "2016-04-27T02:41:58Z", "type": "feedback", "id": "ini99xeity26pl", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>信号量机制允许你把PV操作放在任何代码中&#xff0c;而管程只允许你把PV操作放在管程内部。这种差别可以理解为是否允许你在程序中使用goto语句。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>反问两个问题&#xff1a;你喜欢在程序中使用goto语句吗&#xff1f;为什么&#xff1f;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>现在能理解管程与信号量的区别了吗&#xff1f;</p>"}], "subject": "<p>还不是特别明白&#xff0c;请问为什么管程比信号量好用&#xff0c;<strong>出错的可能小</strong>&#xff0c;找错相对容易一些。感觉并没有任何区别呀&#xff1f;</p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-27T02:49:41Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "created": "2016-04-27T02:49:41Z", "type": "followup", "no_answer": 0, "id": "ini9juuol005mu", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-27T02:53:38Z", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "created": "2016-04-27T02:53:38Z", "type": "feedback", "id": "ini9oxtqcj21tr", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>是的。</p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-27T02:55:48Z", "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "created": "2016-04-27T02:55:48Z", "type": "feedback", "id": "ini9rq27sst1vn", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>OK. 我明白了&#xff0c;谢谢老师&#xff01;</p>"}], "subject": "<p>是的&#xff0c;相比起goto语句&#xff0c;while和for更加安全。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>老师的意思是不是管程的PV语句只允许在lock-&gt;Acquire()和lock-&gt;Realease()中出现&#xff0c;但信号量可以放在任何地方&#xff0c;所以管程比信号量更容易查错&#xff1f;</p>"}, {"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-27T03:29:40Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "i0ccfx63sir1e", "created": "2016-04-27T03:29:40Z", "type": "followup", "no_answer": 0, "id": "iniaz9ms3zk63i", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2016-04-27T03:38:57Z", "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "created": "2016-04-27T03:38:57Z", "type": "feedback", "id": "inibb79nv9v42n", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p>Thx!</p>"}], "subject": "<p>这有提到一些</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cs.mtu.edu/~shene/NSF-3/e-Book/MONITOR/sema-vs-monitor.html\">https://www.cs.mtu.edu/~shene/NSF-3/e-Book/MONITOR/sema-vs-monitor.html</a></p>\n<p></p>"}], "request_instructor_me": false, "nr": 835, "bucket_order": 2, "config": {}, "status": "active", "tags": ["lecture18", "student"], "num_favorites": 0, "bucket_name": "Today", "q_edits": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "request_instructor": 0, "created": "2016-04-25T15:55:37Z", "is_tag_good": false, "type": "question", "s_edits": [], "my_favorite": false, "default_anonymity": "no", "t": 1461771036265, "tag_good": [{"admin_permission": 10, "admin": true, "photo": null, "us": false, "email": "xyong@tsinghua.edu.cn", "class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "清华学生_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "所有老师和助教_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "role": "instructor", "facebook_id": null, "id": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "name": "Yong XIANG"}], "tag_good_arr": ["hdjonbiyfs62ie"], "history": [{"content": "<p>“我们比较基于信号量和管程的实现方案&#xff0c;我们可以看到在管程里头呢&#xff0c;它可以把PV操作都集中到一个模块里头&#xff0c;从而呢简化和降低同步机制的实现难度”&#xff0c;这句话怎么理解&#xff1f;什么叫做“把PV操作都集中到一个模块里头”&#xff1f;为什么又能“简化和降低同步机制的实现难度”&#xff1f;希望有同学能照着下面四幅图予以解答&#xff1a;</p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"6\"><tbody><tr><td><img width=\"463\" height=\"238\" src=\"https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/attach/i5j09fnsl7k5x0/i0b77lptt0s2tg/ing6mkueclzr/信号量.JPG\" /></td><td><img width=\"387\" height=\"230\" src=\"https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/attach/i5j09fnsl7k5x0/i0b77lptt0s2tg/ing6ncno39ec/管程.JPG\" /></td></tr><tr><td><img width=\"460\" height=\"229\" src=\"https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/attach/i5j09fnsl7k5x0/i0b77lptt0s2tg/ing6nyeyvg94/信号量实现.JPG\" /></td><td><img width=\"462\" height=\"230\" src=\"https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/attach/i5j09fnsl7k5x0/i0b77lptt0s2tg/ing6ojkfeivp/管程实现.JPG\" /></td></tr></tbody></table>", "anon": "no", "subject": "18.3管程视频疑问", "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "created": "2016-04-25T16:03:41Z"}, {"content": "<p>“我们比较基于信号量和管程的实现方案&#xff0c;我们可以看到在管程里头呢&#xff0c;它可以把PV操作都集中到一个模块里头&#xff0c;从而呢简化和降低同步机制的实现难度”&#xff0c;这句话怎么理解&#xff1f;什么叫做“把PV操作都集中到一个模块里头”&#xff1f;为什么又能“简化和降低同步机制的实现难度”&#xff1f;希望有同学能照着下面四幅图予以解答&#xff1a;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/attach/i5j09fnsl7k5x0/i0b77lptt0s2tg/ing6mkueclzr/信号量.JPG\" /><img src=\"https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/attach/i5j09fnsl7k5x0/i0b77lptt0s2tg/ing6ncno39ec/管程.JPG\" /><img src=\"https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/attach/i5j09fnsl7k5x0/i0b77lptt0s2tg/ing6nyeyvg94/信号量实现.JPG\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/attach/i5j09fnsl7k5x0/i0b77lptt0s2tg/ing6ojkfeivp/管程实现.JPG\" /></p>", "anon": "no", "subject": "18.3管程视频疑问", "uid": "i0b77lptt0s2tg", "created": "2016-04-25T15:55:37Z"}]}, "error": null}